  "description": "The possum moving at 3am through a suburban yard \u2014 confident in the darkness, unhurried, every footfall deliberate. PLAY DEAD activated at low level, creating a halting breath quality: the sustained note shivers slightly then goes still, then breathes again. Sub oscillator for low-mass presence. Filter nearly closed, warmth pooling in the midrange.",
